&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fix the lock:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class="code postgresql"&gt;&lt;a name="rest_code_e170b37c3cb1482bbe5fd8eb374714bd-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;select&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;pg_cancel_backend&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;pid&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nb"&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Where "pid int" is the pid you find with pg_stat_activity.&lt;/p&gt;
